			<div class="infosubhead"><a name="c_validators"></a>Validators</div>
			<p>We have created a website and API endpoint where anyone can come and validate a badge. They must have access to the badge (or for the API the badge JSON) and they must have separately obtained and confirmed the email address of the person who says it is their badge.</p>
			<br>
